<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TIM1.9">
<l>kīḻā yiṉatuṉpa veḷḷak kaṭaṟaḷḷi yuḷḷuṟappōy</l>
<l>vīḻā tiruntiṉpam vēṇṭumeṉ pīrvira vārpuraṅkaḷ</l>
<l>pāḻā yiṭakkaṇṭa kaṇṭaṉeṇ ṭōḷaṉpaim poṟkaḻalē</l>
<l>tāḻā tiṟaiñcip paṇintupaṉ ṉāḷun talainiṉmiṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You, who say you want pleasure pushing off the ocean with floods of misery</l>
<l>that was before, existing without going to experience the inside [and] falling [into it],</l>
<l>– without despondency bow [and] humbly stay [your] head for many days</l>
<l>at the green-golden anklets of him with eight arms who saw the place of the enemy cities in ruin.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
